<%# Shared partial library (requirement.md §5.14, Phase 3 working process) — ported from
    shopmate-backend's recurring "icon + muted message (+ optional CTA)" empty-state block (same
    template family — e.g. its tenant show page's "No active agreement for this tenant."). Used
    wherever a later phase has nothing yet to list (0 events, 0 participants, ...) instead of a
    bare blank card.

    Locals:
      icon         — String, boxicons suffix (e.g. "bx-calendar-plus")
      message      — String
      action_label — String, optional
      action_path  — String/path, required if action_label is given %>
<div class="text-center py-4">
  <i class="bx <%= icon %> font-size-40 text-muted mb-2 d-block"></i>
  <p class="text-muted mb-<%= local_assigns[:action_label] ? 2 : 0 %>"><%= message %></p>
  <% if local_assigns[:action_label] %>
    <%= link_to action_label, action_path, class: "btn btn-sm btn-primary" %>
  <% end %>
</div>
